Package: vdr-plugin-vaapivideo
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${vdr:Depends}
Description: VAAPI video output plugin for VDR
 Hardware-accelerated video output plugin for VDR using VAAPI decode, DRM
 atomic modesetting, and ALSA audio.
 .
 This plugin drives the display directly through the kernel DRM/KMS
 subsystem -- no X11, Wayland, or OpenGL required.  It runs on a bare
 console, in a systemd service, or headless.
